{
  "stem": "25773.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I will come to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll just finished with my auntie.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went, wanted to find what is with my family going, and my auntie was the first stop.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I entered the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was completely silent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She lived in a flat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were about seven, six flats or eight flats, a big house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was complete silence.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went-- there were no lifts, so I walked to the stairs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Silence.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every door was open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not a person there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I went up to my auntie's place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The door, it was not locked but it was not open.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I pushed it and I found the familiar place that we knew, I knew very well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I screamed, Auntie!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Auntie!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I heard very fine, very faint noise from under the-- there were two enormous cupboards, drawers-- not drawers-- wardrobes, enormous wardrobes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, like in the olden days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And from behind the wardrobes I heard like a faint squealing noise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was sitting my poor grandmother on a wheelchair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grandmother.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wheeled her out, and she told me the whole-- you know, you know it was a traumatic embracing, and crying, and weeping, and asking questions.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she told me that my auntie just the day before, she was-- the Germans came-- which I'll tell you afterwards how they conducted the selections-- and they called everybody down.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she went down with her son, and the husband came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before she went down, she hid my grandmother behind the cupboards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, just thinking she's going to save her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was another auntie who lived there, but she was not at home when the selection took place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she used to come in the evenings still and feed my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
